com.psddev.cms.db

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psddev.dari.db.Record
      • com.psddev.cms.db.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.psddev.dari.db.Recordable, com.psddev.dari.util.HtmlObject, BeanInfo, Cloneable, Comparable<com.psddev.dari.db.Record>

    public class Profile
extends com.psddev.dari.db.Record
    Profile of the entity visiting a CMS-rendered page.

    An instance of this class is created automatically for each page view, and contains information about the visitor that can be used to process pages differently using variations.
